# 🛒 E-commerce Product Discovery – BA Project

This is a Business Analyst case study project developed using Jira, Confluence, and Lucidchart to enhance product search and filtering on an e-commerce platform.

## 📌 Project Overview
Focused on improving customer experience through:
- Advanced keyword search
- Dynamic product filtering (e.g. color, size, brand)
- Smart product-display based on filters

