## 🛠 Tools Used
- 📌 Jira (Agile Project Management)
- 📌 Confluence (Documentation & Requirements)
- 📌 Lucidchart (BPMN Process Flow)

## 🧠 Project Methodology
Agile Scrum with sprint-based planning. Main Epic:  
`EPIC: Enhanced Product Discovery` – improving customer product search and filtering experience.

## 🙋‍♂️ Stakeholders
- Product Owner: PO  
- Business Analyst: Satyam Pandey  
- Developers & QA Team  
- End Users (Customers)
